WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 19=

00:01:17.510 --> 00:01:20.200
So, you are Chancellor Jiang's daughter.

00:01:23.510 --> 00:01:24.350
(Huo Linchuan.)

00:01:26.590 --> 00:01:27.430
Hand him over

00:01:28.590 --> 00:01:29.430
to me.

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:34.000
(I did it.)

00:01:34.200 --> 00:01:35.590
(Just as the immortal foretold,)

00:01:36.070 --> 00:01:38.150
(I'm the variable
in Huo Linchuan's fate.)

00:01:45.590 --> 00:01:46.870
(Huo Linchuan,)

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:48.070
(Father, Mother,)

00:01:48.590 --> 00:01:51.230
(I will change the ending this time.)

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:53.480
Step aside.

00:01:55.430 --> 00:01:56.560
Why capture my father?

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:00.950
My father is the Duke,

00:02:01.230 --> 00:02:02.710
yet he's been wrongfully imprisoned.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.040
Tell me. Who stands to gain?

00:02:05.510 --> 00:02:06.643
Other than Chancellor Jiang,

00:02:07.150 --> 00:02:08.960
who else

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:09.840
is so powerful?

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:13.120
(Why would he falsely accuse my father?)

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:15.240
(Has he forgotten me?)

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:17.800
Mr. Huo.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.560
Please, discern the truth.

00:02:24.910 --> 00:02:28.960
There must be some schemer behind this.

00:02:30.190 --> 00:02:32.400
I have served for over 30 years.

00:02:32.750 --> 00:02:34.430
My life has always been one of caution.

00:02:34.590 --> 00:02:37.680
How would I dare frame the Duke?

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.520
Huo...

00:02:42.910 --> 00:02:43.840
Mr. Huo.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.000
Baseless words mean nothing.

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:46.520
Such recklessness is unlike you.

00:02:47.150 --> 00:02:48.400
You have not a shred of proof.

00:02:48.630 --> 00:02:50.910
How can you declare my father guilty?

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:54.150
You must've been deceived by a traitor.

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.080
(Huo Linchuan,)

00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.840
(have you truly lost all your memories?)

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:04.000
You don't believe me?

00:03:09.630 --> 00:03:10.750
The proof you wanted.

00:03:15.630 --> 00:03:17.076
On the day my father was imprisoned,

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:18.910
800,000 taels of silver

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:22.120
went into the Auspice Shop
of your family.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.360
This is your family's ledger.

00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:27.380
Do I still need to cross-check with you?

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.800
(Such a carefully laid trap)

00:03:31.630 --> 00:03:33.276
(doesn't seem
like Huo Linchuan's doing.)

00:03:34.240 --> 00:03:35.360
(Could it be Jiang Huaikang?)

00:03:36.240 --> 00:03:37.360
(Or perhaps Lu Huaijin?)

00:03:38.360 --> 00:03:39.400
The evidence is undeniable.

00:03:39.910 --> 00:03:41.190
Do you have anything else to say?

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.280
Please, judge wisely.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:49.560
I entrusted the Auspice Shop

00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:52.150
to someone else three years ago.

00:03:52.430 --> 00:03:54.840
I rarely check its accounts.

00:03:55.910 --> 00:03:59.750
Someone is killing two birds
with one stone

00:04:00.430 --> 00:04:01.840
by framing Duke Huo

00:04:02.030 --> 00:04:04.840
and dragging me into disgrace.

00:04:06.630 --> 00:04:07.470
Father.

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:10.080
Mr. Huo,

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:12.000
how can you be sure it was my father,

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:14.710
just based on a ledger?

00:04:14.710 --> 00:04:15.550
Guards.

00:04:16.390 --> 00:04:17.230
Mr. Huo,

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.640
to harm my parents,

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:21.466
you'll have to step over my body first.

00:04:28.750 --> 00:04:29.590
No!

00:04:29.830 --> 00:04:30.920
Let go of my daughter!

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:32.600
Let go of her!

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:33.440
Mr. Huo.

00:04:35.090 --> 00:04:36.070
- Mr. Huo.
- No!

00:04:36.070 --> 00:04:37.870
Kill me if you must.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:39.270
Spare my daughter.

00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:41.190
She has nothing to do with this.

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.430
Let go of my daughter!

00:04:43.430 --> 00:04:44.510
Mr. Huo!

00:04:44.680 --> 00:04:45.760
- Huo Linchuan.
- Don't!

00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:47.080
My father...

00:04:47.490 --> 00:04:48.420
No!

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.870
He's innocent.

00:04:57.630 --> 00:04:58.560
Yanzhi!

00:04:58.560 --> 00:04:59.400
Stop!

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:01.240
Ruoli!

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:02.080
Are you all right?

00:05:03.950 --> 00:05:04.790
I'm fine.

00:05:05.630 --> 00:05:06.510
As I told you,

00:05:07.190 --> 00:05:08.870
I'll handle this myself.

00:05:10.070 --> 00:05:11.160
I don't need your help.

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:13.566
I know you're anxious to save Father,

00:05:13.830 --> 00:05:15.240
but the truth isn't clear yet.

00:05:15.460 --> 00:05:16.866
(Ledger)
You mustn't act so rashly.

00:05:17.510 --> 00:05:18.830
Don't lose your calm.

00:05:20.750 --> 00:05:21.590
Mr. Huo,

00:05:22.360 --> 00:05:24.070
this ledger

00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:25.000
is a fake.

00:05:26.390 --> 00:05:27.270
What?

00:05:27.430 --> 00:05:29.870
(Ledger)
Every entry of the shop is recorded.

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:34.390
Yours should end
on the 5th of the 7th month,

00:05:34.920 --> 00:05:37.510
yet it includes entries from the 15th.

00:05:38.190 --> 00:05:41.360
This ledger must've been fabricated.

00:05:50.560 --> 00:05:51.400
Two days.

00:05:52.120 --> 00:05:52.960
Give me two days.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:55.950
I'll surely prove my father's innocence.

00:05:56.950 --> 00:05:57.790
Alright.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:05:59.800
Then I'll grant you two days.

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:01.160
After two days,

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:02.310
if you fail to present proof,

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:05.390
your whole family will pay the price.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:10.760
Yuan.

00:06:11.240 --> 00:06:12.110
Yuan.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:12.960
Are you alright?

00:06:14.360 --> 00:06:15.200
Mother.

00:06:15.430 --> 00:06:16.270
Father.

00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:26.300
(Tongchen Inn)

00:06:38.390 --> 00:06:39.310
No!

00:06:39.430 --> 00:06:40.560
Let go of my daughter!

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:41.430
Mr. Huo.

00:06:41.430 --> 00:06:42.800
Let go of her!

00:06:42.950 --> 00:06:43.990
- Huo Linchuan.
- Mr. Huo!

00:06:44.870 --> 00:06:45.870
- My father...
- Don't!

00:06:47.510 --> 00:06:49.310
He's innocent.

00:06:53.140 --> 00:06:55.360
(Why do I feel this way?)

00:07:05.240 --> 00:07:06.160
Huai'an, Shuanghua,

00:07:06.390 --> 00:07:07.800
you're finally back.

00:07:08.480 --> 00:07:10.360
Thank heavens.

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:13.430
I heard you were ambushed
outside the city.

00:07:13.720 --> 00:07:15.390
I was so worried about you.

00:07:15.630 --> 00:07:16.720
Were you hurt at all?

00:07:18.560 --> 00:07:19.400
It's nothing serious.

00:07:20.630 --> 00:07:21.470
Father.

00:07:23.390 --> 00:07:24.390
It's fine.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:28.190
Uncle, you didn't just run fast.

00:07:29.510 --> 00:07:32.720
You also got the news
quicker than anyone.

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:34.440
Yuan.

00:07:34.630 --> 00:07:36.240
My parents returned home safely.

00:07:36.240 --> 00:07:37.630
That's their good fortune.

00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:41.040
It must've disappointed those hiding

00:07:41.310 --> 00:07:42.920
in the shadows, waiting to profit

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:44.120
from others' misfortune.

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:44.960
Yuan.

00:07:45.310 --> 00:07:46.150
Yes, yes.

00:07:46.390 --> 00:07:48.600
You two are both safe.

00:07:48.750 --> 00:07:49.870
You're truly blessed.

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:51.360
Tomorrow,

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:53.430
I'll go to the Huo Mansion

00:07:53.870 --> 00:07:56.270
to ask for an explanation.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:58.190
- You mustn't do that.
- Tomorrow?

00:07:58.720 --> 00:08:00.240
We might lose our lives before then.

00:08:01.720 --> 00:08:03.920
No need to trouble you.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:04.860
I'll handle it myself.

00:08:06.510 --> 00:08:07.360
Sure.

00:08:07.390 --> 00:08:10.480
Huai'an, Shuanghua, please rest first.

00:08:10.750 --> 00:08:12.190
I'll make the arrangements.

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:20.240
You child.

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:23.310
How can you speak
to your uncle like that?

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.080
Father.

00:08:26.540 --> 00:08:29.100
(Jiang Mansion)

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:33.080
Father.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.840
Father.

00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:39.590
Yuan,

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:41.870
why haven't you gone to rest yet?

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:44.030
Mother was frightened today.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:46.720
I just served her a calming soup.

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:47.870
She finally fell asleep.

00:08:48.600 --> 00:08:49.510
This

00:08:51.630 --> 00:08:52.600
is my fault.

00:08:53.550 --> 00:08:54.849
I failed to manage the household,

00:08:55.960 --> 00:08:58.000
so this misfortune came upon us,

00:08:58.870 --> 00:09:00.870
making you and your mother suffer.

00:09:01.320 --> 00:09:02.160
Father,

00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:03.539
everything happened so suddenly.

00:09:03.550 --> 00:09:04.390
It's not your fault.

00:09:05.750 --> 00:09:06.630
What happened today

00:09:07.200 --> 00:09:08.390
feels rather suspicious.

00:09:10.790 --> 00:09:13.030
Yuan, why do you say that?

00:09:14.790 --> 00:09:16.790
The two clans weren't close,

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:18.313
but there weren't old grudges.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:20.600
Yet once Duke Huo was in trouble,

00:09:21.030 --> 00:09:23.200
all blame fell on us alone.

00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:26.510
Besides, the evidence Mr. Huo presented

00:09:26.790 --> 00:09:29.600
was merely the shop accounts
you no longer managed.

00:09:29.790 --> 00:09:31.240
So calculated at every step.

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:33.390
It's truly suspicious.

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:36.440
You...

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:40.150
You think someone's sowing discord?

00:09:41.910 --> 00:09:42.840
Not just that.

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:44.750
At the lantern fair,

00:09:44.790 --> 00:09:46.000
we were ambushed.

00:09:46.390 --> 00:09:48.790
Yet the Huos knew where we were.

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:51.360
There must be an insider

00:09:51.790 --> 00:09:53.840
who leaked our whereabouts.

00:09:55.670 --> 00:09:56.510
Father,

00:09:56.630 --> 00:09:57.790
I have a plan.

00:10:12.220 --> 00:10:15.820
(Jiang Mansion)

00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:17.510
(Huo Linchuan,)

00:10:18.150 --> 00:10:19.360
(why don't you remember me?)

00:10:23.910 --> 00:10:24.750
No!

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:26.080
Let go of my daughter!

00:10:26.080 --> 00:10:26.960
Mr. Huo.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:27.800
Let go of her!

00:10:33.910 --> 00:10:35.510
You are the mistress of the Huo clan.

00:10:36.360 --> 00:10:38.120
And you are my wife.

00:10:48.030 --> 00:10:48.870
Ruyan,

00:10:49.550 --> 00:10:50.550
it's been so long.

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:52.080
Don't you miss me?

00:10:52.750 --> 00:10:54.720
Look at your delicate face.

00:10:55.550 --> 00:10:57.103
Master Huaikang, please don't do this.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:58.200
Ruyan.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:10:59.560
Ruyan?

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.320
Yes, milady.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:04.000
Master Huaikang, I shall take my leave.

00:11:14.750 --> 00:11:16.550
Milady, you were frightened.

00:11:16.630 --> 00:11:18.630
Have a bowl of calming soup.

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:20.240
How thoughtful of you.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:22.120
Milady,

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:23.790
it's what I ought to do.

00:11:25.670 --> 00:11:28.390
Mr. Lu sent these lanterns.

00:11:28.910 --> 00:11:31.720
He said you liked them
at the lantern fair.

00:11:33.870 --> 00:11:34.710
Ruyan,

00:11:35.750 --> 00:11:37.080
though you're my maid,

00:11:37.910 --> 00:11:39.910
I've always seen you as my dear sister.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.750
If you ever feel wronged,

00:11:42.750 --> 00:11:43.870
you must tell me right away.

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:46.750
Even if the sky falls,
I'll bear it for you.

00:11:48.630 --> 00:11:49.510
Thanks, milady.

00:11:52.030 --> 00:11:53.270
Go back and rest.

00:11:53.360 --> 00:11:54.200
Yes,

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:06.560
Mr. Huo,

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:08.270
this ledger

00:12:08.960 --> 00:12:09.800
is a fake.

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:12.160
What?

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:15.240
(Ledger)
Every entry of the shop is recorded.

00:12:15.670 --> 00:12:18.030
Yours should end
on the 5th of the 7th month,

00:12:18.840 --> 00:12:21.360
yet it includes entries from the 15th.

00:12:22.030 --> 00:12:25.080
This ledger must've been fabricated.

00:12:35.510 --> 00:12:36.350
(Lu Huaijin,)

00:12:36.870 --> 00:12:37.870
(I actually believed)

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:40.030
(that playing this deep-affection act
with you)

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:42.150
(could save my parents' lives.)

00:12:43.750 --> 00:12:45.550
What a fine show of devotion,

00:12:46.030 --> 00:12:47.480
Yunzhou.

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.480
♪The dream shattered♪

00:13:11.840 --> 00:13:13.520
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:15.160
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:13:16.040 --> 00:13:17.600
♪How vague♪

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:19.520
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:13:19.520 --> 00:13:21.760
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:25.160
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:13:25.640 --> 00:13:28.480
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:33.880
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:36.000
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:39.960
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:42.240
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:13:42.640 --> 00:13:46.360
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:49.920
♪Life after life♪

00:13:50.400 --> 00:13:53.080
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:57.800
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:13:57.880 --> 00:14:00.920
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:14:01.080 --> 00:14:02.480
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:14:02.480 --> 00:14:05.600
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:07.120
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:14:07.240 --> 00:14:11.000
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:14:11.720 --> 00:14:14.520
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:17.640
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:22.360
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:14:22.600 --> 00:14:25.520
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:14:25.640 --> 00:14:30.080
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:14:30.280 --> 00:14:36.000
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:14:36.440 --> 00:14:39.160
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:14:39.400 --> 00:14:42.120
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:14:42.560 --> 00:14:48.560
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪